<div class="row">
  <div class="col-md-3">
    <h4>About the Author</h4>
    <p style="text-align: right;">Hi! My name is Alyssa and I am a native North Carolinian who currently resides in Portland. I earned a B.A. in Classical Studies with a concentration on Ancient Greek and Latin from the University of North Carolina at Asheville in the beautiful Blue Ridge Mountains. Currently, I am attending Epicodus -- a four month coding bootcamp that focuses on pair programming. This blog is a mashup of lingustics and web development with a general shower-thoughts vibe. Other things that may come to light: my love for yoga and trail running, a strange obsession with knitting.</p>

    <hr>

    <h4>Tags for Days</h4>
    <% if @tags.any? %>
      <ul style="list-style:none;">
        <% @tags.each do |tag| %>
          <li><%= link_to "#{tag.description}", tag_path(tag) %></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <p>No tags yet.</p>
    <% end %>

    <hr>

    <% if current_user %>
      <%= link_to "New Tag", new_tag_path, class: 'btn btn-small btn-default' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>

  <div class="col-md-9">
    <% if @posts.any? %>
    <h3>Recent Posts</h3>
      <ul style="list-style:none;">
        <% @posts.each do |post| %>
          <li><h3><%= link_to "#{post.title}", post_path(post) %></h3></li>
          <li>Posted on <%= post.created_at.to_formatted_s(:long) %></li>
          <li><p><%= post.content %></p></li>
          <ul style="list-style:none;">
            <% post.tags.each do |t| %>
              <li><%= link_to "#{t.description}", tag_path(t) %></li>
            <% end %>
          </ul>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    <% else %>
      <p>No posts yet.</p>
    <% end %>

    <hr>
    <% if current_user %>
      <%= link_to "New Post", new_post_path, class: 'btn btn-small btn-default' %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
